    <img src="/mbimagespng/scholarship.png"><span class="maintext">

<h1>Scholarship</h1>

<ol type=1><p>

<li>Show proof that you have been in attendance at school (elementary, high school, evening vocational, or night school) for a period of at least one year.<p>

<li>Present evidence from your teacher or principal that during this period - your attendance has been satisfactory, that you have had an average of 82, and you have no grade below 75 in any subject.<p>

<li>Present evidence that you have taken a satisfactory part in the life of your school.<p>

<li>Give evidence of at least five instances where your school training has been of value to you in Scouting and other activities or interest outside of school.<p>

<li>Give evidence that you have made use of educational resources other than those of your school for self-education.<p>

<li>Present evidence that your behavior, leadership, and service have been better than average.</ol>

</span><p>
